data.description: Welcome to your private sanctuary in the highly sought-after North Hampton Golf Community. This spectacular 5 bed/ 3.5 bath home is situated on an oversize lot bordered by a wooded preservation area. With gorgeous mahogany wood floors and a spacious open floor plan, your family room opens to a covered lanai and outdoor kitchen w/bar seating. Retreat to your screened-in heated pool, spa, fire pit & full outdoor bathroom in your secluded, fenced-in yard. Ample room for entertaining with a formal dining room, gourmet kitchen w/ induction stove & double oven, spacious family room + office on the main floor. The primary suite has double vanities w/ separate shower & soaking tub, custom closet + private 12x18 screened lanai & 12x18 open sun deck. New roof & flooring upstairs 2023, new HVACs & water heater in 2021, new lanai screen in 2022. North Hampton Golf Club has an Arnold Palmer designed course, kayak launch, community pool, tennis & pickle ball courts, basketball courts and playground.
